<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-10-23T14:05:02-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-10-23T14:05:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T14:05:02-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime 会员现在可以节省汽油费</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、橙色和棕褐色背景上的亚马逊徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4zO0UmME3uC9fMHRjqRPvBYWasI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73673151/acastro_STK103__01.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊正在优化 Prime 优惠。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;37mRIM&quot;>;Amazon Prime 会员为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aboutamazon.com/news/retail/amazon-gas- saving-prime&quot;>;获得新福利&lt;/a>;：加油时额外节省。通过将您的亚马逊账户与 BP 的忠诚度计划关联起来，每当您在参与计划的 BP 加油站加油时，您就可以节省每加仑 10 美分。顺便说一句，它的折扣很像 &lt;a href=&quot;https://corporate.walmart.com/news/2022/04/27/walmart-increases-fuel-discount-and-expands-to-exxon-and-mobil- Stations-pumping-additional- savings-into-member-wallets&quot;>;沃尔玛通过其 Prime 竞争对手计划 Walmart Plus 在埃克森加油站提供的服务&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;IRD7g6&quot;>;当然，您需要同意让 BP &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bp.com%2Fen_us%2Funited-states%2Fhome %2F产品和服务%2Fearnify%2Fearnify-privacy-statement.html%23accordion_collecting-personal-data&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F23%2F24277750 %2Famazon-prime-bp-earnify- savings-fuel-rewards&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;收集有关您的信息&lt;/a>;以获得折扣。但再加入一项忠诚度计划有什么坏处呢？如果英国石油公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/business-64544110&quot;>;放弃其碳排放目标&lt;/a>;以实现利润最大化&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2021/8/9/22613531/climate-change-united-nations-report-extreme-weather-ipcc&quot;>;当地球燃烧时&lt;/a>;？&lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;因为有资本主义下没有道德消费，而且最近所有东西都太贵了，我继续......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23 /24277750/amazon-prime-bp-earnify- savings-fuel-rewards&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277750/amazon-prime-bp-earnify-savings-fuel-rewards" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277750/amazon-prime-bp-earnify- savings-fuel-rewards</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T13:54:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T13:54:52-04:00</updated><title>一项调查揭露数据经纪人使用广告来帮助跟踪几乎所有手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;被其他眼睛包围的大眼睛的插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XKw4C0p_ernoUoXyXQzKpFDD9B0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73673105/acastro_190204_1777_privacy_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;R97rXM&quot;>;一项调查由据 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/inside-the-us-government-bought-tool-that- can-track-phones-at-abortion-clinics/&quot;>;来自 &lt;em>;404 Media 的报告&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://krebsonsecurity.com/2024/10/the-global- Monitoring-free-for-all-in-mobile-ad-data/?ref=404media.co&quot;>;和 &lt;em>;Krebs 谈安全&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。据报道，这项名为 Locate X 的人员追踪服务允许用户使用其移动广告标识符（分配给手机的唯一编号）来跟踪设备。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;qlGLys&quot;>;总部位于新泽西州的 Atlas Data Privacy Corp据 &lt;em>;404 称，旨在帮助人们从数据经纪人那里删除个人信息的组织发现，该软件能够在地图上显示手机的位置，允许任何有权访问的人跨州追踪某人的精确位置。媒体&lt;/em>;。然后，这些信息可用于确定特定的手机...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277679/atlas-privacy-babel -street-data-brokers-locate-x-tracking&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277679/atlas-privacy-babel-street-data-brokers-locate-x-tracking" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277679/atlas-privacy-babel-street-data-brokers-locate-x-tracking</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T13:43:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T13:43:09-04:00</updated><title>苹果的第一个 iOS 18.2 Beta 版增加了更多 AI 功能和 ChatGPT 集成</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;WWDC 2024 在 iOS 上集成 ChatGPT 的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ARdhoIIf7UU1lZEul-DmCJGAIag=/0x0:1306x871/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73673077/Apple_WWDC24_Apple_Intelligence_Siri_ChatGPT_request_240 610.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;XZIzIj&quot;>;Apple 现在让开发者尝试更多 Apple Intelligence 功能。该公司发布了 iOS 18.2 的第一个开发者测试版，它增加了一些工具，例如使用 Genmoji 生成表情符号、使用 Image Playground 生成图像、更多人工智能驱动的书写功能、与 ChatGPT 的集成、使用 iPhone 上的相机进行搜索的视觉智能等工具16 部手机，以及更多，&lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5mac.com/2024/10/23/ios-18-2-beta-out-now-apple-intelligence-features/&quot;>;根据&lt;em>; 9to5Mac&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。通过此测试版，现已支持 Apple Intelligence &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5mac.com/2024/10/23/ios-18-2-brings-apple-intelligence-support-to-more-regions/&quot;>;更多地区也将推出&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NS0kDF&quot;>;iOS 18.2 将为用户带来第二批 Apple Intelligence 功能。第一批包括稍微智能的 Siri 和通知摘要等功能，设置为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/6/24263398/ios-18-iphone-16-apple -intelligence-coming-october-update-ai-notification-summaries&quot;>;下周推出&lt;/a>;，正式发布 iOS 18.1。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;c7zwjk&quot;>;Apple 首次推出了计划中的 Apple.. .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277811/apple-intelligence-ios-18-2-beta-chatgpt-visual-intelligence-image -代&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277811/apple-intelligence-ios-18-2-beta-chatgpt-visual-intelligence-image-generation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277811/apple-intelligence-ios-18-2-beta-chatgpt-visual-intelligence-image- Generation</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T13:06:12-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T13:06:12-04:00</updated><title>苹果和高盛因误导 Apple Card 持卡人被罚款数百万美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黄色和青色背景上的 Apple 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/95zgRIWECX2OpZVIwCaHejyJX8k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73672977/STK071_apple_K_Radtke_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GONl2q&quot;>;消费者金融保护局 (CFPB) 宣布&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.consumerfinance.gov/about- us/newsroom/cfpb-orders-apple-and-goldman-sachs-to-pay-over-89million-for-apple-card-failures/&quot;>;对苹果和高盛罚款总计 8900 万美元&lt;/a>;，因为这些公司“非法地错误地处理了交易纠纷，并在无息支付选项方面误导了 iPhone 购买者”。 CFPB 表示，这些问题影响了“数十万 Apple Card 用户”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Zlpoq6&quot;>;据 CFPB 称，苹果并未向高盛发送“数以万计”的 Apple Card 交易纠纷。消费者保护局。 CFPB 表示，高盛也没有根据联邦法律及时完成对其收到的争议的调查。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bvTnIX&quot;>;持卡人还被引导相信他们会自动获得免息。如果他们使用 Apple Card 购买 Apple 设备，则可以获得融资，但是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277710/apple-goldman-sachs -cfpb-fine-charge-disputes-system&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277710/apple-goldman-sachs-cfpb-fine-charge-disputes-system" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277710/apple-goldman-sachs-cfpb-fine-charge-disputes-system</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T12:36:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T12:36:26-04:00</updated><title>最适合训练和日常生活的 Garmin 手表</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;彩色背景上的几款 Garmin 手表&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5dtgeyIVuFtgCeI1hMNSF_9Epo=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72245384/236645_Buying_Guide_Garmin_Watches_WJoel.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Garmins 不再只是多项运动的庞然大物。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Will Joel / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Garmin 可能以其硬核健身手表而闻名，但它也提供广泛的生活方式产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T12:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T12:30:00-04:00</updated><title>三星坚固耐用的 Galaxy Watch Ultra 已降至迄今为止最优惠的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Galaxy Watch Ultra 特写&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WCazJaNFDsttf4YfEIxQUvrZj1k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73672820/gwultra_9.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 是我们最喜欢的健身追踪器之一，目前在亚马逊最高可享受 150 美元折扣。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DCNIah&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24211888/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-review- smartwatch-wearables&quot;>;三星 Galaxy Watch 7&lt;/a>; 是一款不错的 Android 智能手表，特别是如果您已经嵌入三星的生态系统，但它最适合休闲健身追踪。如果您喜欢户外活动，或者只是想要市场上功能最齐全的三星智能手表，&lt;strong>;三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra &lt;/strong>;是更好的选择 - 目前&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .amazon.com/SAMSUNG-Smartwatch-Wellness-Tracking-Manufacturer/dp/B0D1YLBBMB?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊有售&lt;/a>;，起价新最低价为 499.99 美元（折扣 150 美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;AVqDsk&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data- anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;现在最值得购买的健身追踪