/nonscamera.com/products/nons-sl660&quot;>;Nons SL660&lt;/a>;镜头。无论哪种情况，它仍然会受到即时胶片的局限性的阻碍。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;O3W5Oe&quot;>;那些升级的光学器件的价格要高得多。 Lomo&#39;Instant Wide Glass 现已上市，售价 279 美元，而全塑料 &lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.lomography.com/us/lomo-instant-wide-camera-black-edition&quot;>;Lomo&#39;拍立得广角相机黑色版&lt;/a>;仍为 169 美元。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://instax.com/wide400/en/&quot;>;Fujifilm 自己的 Instax Wide 400&lt;/a>; 甚至更便宜......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277617/lomography-lomo-instant-wide-glass-camera-photography-fujifilm-instax-wide&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277617/lomography-lomo-instant-wide-glass-camera-photography-fujifilm-instax-wide" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/23/24277617/lomography-lomo-instant-wide-glass-camera-photography-fujifilm-instax-wide</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-23T11:40:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-23T11:40:49-04:00</updated><title>类似智能手机的 Boox Palma 电子书阅读器价格创下历史新低</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人在水边使用类似智能手机的设备的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hLtV3EldCi2WawGq6ZJAQshDnnk=/125x0:1475x900/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73672619/Boox_Palma_lead.5.jpeg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Boox Palma 无论是黑色还是白色看起来都很光滑。&lt;/em>; |图片：Boox&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X3TmK4&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/16/24271603/kindle-2024-colorsoft-scribe- paperwhite-specs-price-date&quot;>;Kindle&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/4/24158251/kobo-libra-clara-colour-e-reader- review&quot;>;Kobos 使用起来相对舒适，但如果它们太大且限制性太大，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24184777/boox-palma-e-ink-smartphone -reader&quot;>;类似智能手机的 &lt;strong>;Boox Palma&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; 是一个极好的替代方案，我们对它的兴趣非常浓厚。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theve